<task id="registering_brokers">
	<title>Register VMware Broker</title>
    <shortdesc/>
    <taskbody>
        <context>
        	<draft-comment>Include with CC section?</draft-comment>
        	<note type="tip">If you arenâ€™t using VMware, skip this section.</note>
        </context>
        <steps>
            <step>
            	<cmd>On one of the CLCs, register the primary VMware Broker by entering the following command:</cmd>
            	<info>
            		<codeblock>/usr/sbin/euca_conf --register-vmwarebroker --partition=zone00 
            		--host=&lt;CC_#1_IP_address> --component=vmwarebroker00</codeblock>
            		<note type="important">Register the VMware Broker component using the CC IP address, not the CLC IP address.</note>
            	</info>
            </step>
        	<step>
        		<cmd>Register the secondary VMware Broker by entering the following command:</cmd>
        		<info>
        			<codeblock>/usr/sbin/euca_conf --register-vmwarebroker --partition=zone00 
	--host=&lt;CC_#2_IP_address> --component=vmwarebroker01</codeblock>
        		</info>
        	</step>
        </steps>
    </taskbody>
</task>
